bool cvmx_sfp_mod_info::fec_required

Set to true if forward error correction is required, for example, a 25GBase-CR CA-S cable.

FEC should only be disabled at 25G with CA-N cables. FEC is required with 5M and longer cables.

bool cvmx_sfp_mod_info::internal_cdr

True if internal retimer or clock and data recovery circuit.
